      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (E/uval) must be below 1.96 for all QoIs; percent difference must be below 10%.",
      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy acceptance criteria. Maximum E/uval = 1.44 (yield force, pooled); maximum percent difference = 7.1% (yield force). Validation uncertainty computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 5 including experimental measurement uncertainty and model parameter uncertainty."
